      <title>意大利外长梅洛尼致力于在美国大选前修复与习近平的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/italy-s-meloni-on-mission-to-mend-ties-with-xi-ahead-of-us-vote</link>
