      <title>全球性别平等倒退危及欧盟愿景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/global-backsliding-on-gender-parity-puts-eu-ambitions-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于世界各国政府和布鲁塞尔的权力掮客们不愿做出引人注目的平等承诺，欧盟执行机构将无法实现其最高级别成员国中性别平衡的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-27/global-backsliding-on-gender-parity-puts-eu-ambitions-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Jul 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
